				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Slashing - 1HB - Piercing<a name="75525"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Apr 18 05 3:23 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>THis is kinda lame but to raise weapon skills I grab a yellow and kite it down till it runs. Get a quick low damage weapon. then chain the mob as it runs. Next just attack. when it gets down to 2% i usually charm it and tell it to sit so it gains HPs faster. Gets back up to 18 start chaining and melee again.
<br />

<br />
I like yellows cause you wont hit them as much as a blue. 
